{"lang":"de","stage":7,"title":"fuller sentences","sentences":[{"t":"Er sucht seit März einen Job.","en":"He's been looking for a job since March.","a":"n_53f62b97743e.mp3"},{"t":"Macht zusammen dreißig Euro.","en":"It all comes to thirty euros.","a":"n_3eb5633798f6.mp3"},{"t":"Wir essen um eins.","en":"We eat at one.","a":"n_01d2ee61a1af.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab um fünf Feierabend.","en":"I finish at five.","a":"n_2afe240d4822.mp3"},{"t":"Sonntags schlaf ich viel.","en":"On Sundays I sleep a lot.","a":"n_d09d68b29cbe.mp3"},{"t":"Samstags arbeite ich nicht.","en":"I don't work on Saturday.","a":"n_ee76c3f1cb22.mp3"},{"t":"Bis Donnerstag.","en":"See you on Thursday.","a":"n_70e518c7c8e8.mp3"},{"t":"Wann fangen wir an?","en":"What time do we start?","a":"n_8486cee37da4.mp3"},{"t":"Heute hab ich Geburtstag.","en":"Today is my birthday.","a":"n_8ce0ef2a0e17.mp3"},{"t":"Du bist wieder spät dran.","en":"You're late again.","a":"n_da7aed2a68d1.mp3"},{"t":"Was kosten die beiden?","en":"How much are the two of them?","a":"n_7f9efc4b60e1.mp3"},{"t":"Für wie viel verkaufst du's?","en":"How much are you selling it for?","a":"n_22221268f96b.mp3"},{"t":"Heute ist der Eintritt frei.","en":"Getting in is free today.","a":"n_5178befc43af.mp3"},{"t":"Mein Bauch tut weh.","en":"My stomach hurts.","a":"n_9722454a7833.mp3"},{"t":"Mein Rücken tut weh.","en":"My back hurts.","a":"n_131a144e178d.mp3"},{"t":"Meine Augen tun weh.","en":"My eyes hurt.","a":"n_baeb1655827a.mp3"},{"t":"Ich stell dir Ana vor.","en":"Let me introduce you to Ana.","a":"n_9fc5a66f5172.mp3"},{"t":"Zu Hause langweil ich mich.","en":"I'm bored at home.","a":"n_3add99fbe08e.mp3"},{"t":"Sie braucht mehr Geld.","en":"She needs more money.","a":"n_fcf362bcbd81.mp3"},{"t":"Ich kann's später sehen.","en":"I can see it later.","a":"n_ad6bfe0a7e21.mp3"},{"t":"Kommst du mit oder bleibst du?","en":"Are you coming or staying?","a":"n_84f1424658d2.mp3"},{"t":"Sie macht Abendessen.","en":"She's making dinner.","a":"n_16bb5c56b1cf.mp3"},{"t":"Ich frag nur kurz was.","en":"I'll ask a quick question.","a":"n_14132f49936b.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab gestern Abend meine Tasche gepackt.","en":"I packed my bag last night.","a":"n_8ade2e017f5a.mp3"},{"t":"Bring mich nicht zum Lachen.","en":"Don't make me laugh.","a":"n_03b9cc30fa03.mp3"},{"t":"Ich erzähl's dir später.","en":"I'll tell you about it later.","a":"n_d434a9ef66d9.mp3"},{"t":"Wer hat's dir gesagt?","en":"Who told you?","a":"n_51e486697e9c.mp3"},{"t":"Du sagst mir nie was.","en":"You never tell me anything.","a":"n_fd8d6c8db529.mp3"},{"t":"Ich kenn das Restaurant nicht.","en":"I don't know that restaurant.","a":"n_a9de1306950d.mp3"},{"t":"Ich seh den Unterschied nicht.","en":"I don't see the difference.","a":"n_3db348870d7d.mp3"},{"t":"Ich will dir was zeigen.","en":"I want to show you something.","a":"n_0bc85f553535.mp3"},{"t":"Schau mich nicht so an.","en":"Don't look at me like that.","a":"n_7c7f06295ff0.mp3"},{"t":"Wir arbeiten diese Woche viel.","en":"We're working a lot this week.","a":"n_9bf0bebd443b.mp3"},{"t":"Kannst du mir das Brot reichen?","en":"Can you pass me the bread?","a":"n_4b633f08c589.mp3"},{"t":"Meine Freunde wohnen in der Nähe.","en":"My friends live nearby.","a":"n_b2be6a05c0a2.mp3"},{"t":"Wir fangen um vier an.","en":"We start at four.","a":"n_19e690adc4b3.mp3"},{"t":"Im Dezember ist es kalt.","en":"It's cold in December.","a":"n_8a052969bf26.mp3"},{"t":"Meine Uhr geht falsch.","en":"My watch is wrong.","a":"n_f915bf8263db.mp3"},{"t":"Ich erklär's dir später.","en":"I'll explain later.","a":"n_9c657dc84c25.mp3"},{"t":"Ich bin heute spät aufgestanden.","en":"I got up late today.","a":"n_f23f2677d678.mp3"},{"t":"Du bist genau pünktlich.","en":"You're right on time.","a":"n_fa24ff957bf0.mp3"},{"t":"Kann ich mit Karte zahlen?","en":"Can I pay by card?","a":"n_855e1a74a6c9.mp3"},{"t":"Wo halt ich das Taxi an?","en":"Where do I stop the taxi?","a":"n_416309ffef10.mp3"},{"t":"Ich verpass immer den Zug.","en":"I always miss the train.","a":"n_ae7bdd12159b.mp3"},{"t":"Einer meiner Zähne tut weh.","en":"One of my teeth hurts.","a":"n_b942e19e3d59.mp3"},{"t":"Gestern war ich im Kino.","en":"Yesterday I went to the movies.","a":"n_57bf243e7439.mp3"},{"t":"Meine Füße tun weh.","en":"My feet hurt.","a":"n_9950b163d8ed.mp3"},{"t":"Schau dich im Spiegel an.","en":"Look at yourself in the mirror.","a":"n_fe4d43dc4b7e.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab's noch nie probiert.","en":"I've never tried it.","a":"n_9ed17f22625e.mp3"},{"t":"Wo warst du am Samstag?","en":"Where did you go on Saturday?","a":"n_cfed00d8423c.mp3"},{"t":"Du musst was essen.","en":"You have to eat something.","a":"n_a432b3391ee8.mp3"},{"t":"Nein, das bin ich nicht.","en":"No, that's not me.","a":"n_b5f1febb3fbe.mp3"},{"t":"Mir geht's gut, und dir?","en":"I'm good, and you?","a":"n_f44fc3f95ce3.mp3"},{"t":"Ich mach, was ich will.","en":"I do what I want.","a":"n_dce264455110.mp3"},{"t":"Ich mach, was ich kann.","en":"I do what I can.","a":"n_53e6f9d4e8c6.mp3"},{"t":"Du musst mehr schlafen.","en":"You have to sleep more.","a":"n_6438f0436d3e.mp3"},{"t":"Musst du morgen arbeiten?","en":"Do you have to work tomorrow?","a":"n_1eda0f038add.mp3"},{"t":"Schau, was ich hab.","en":"Look what I've got.","a":"n_9397eee16ad3.mp3"},{"t":"Ja, hier tut's weh.","en":"Yes, it hurts here.","a":"n_edb645552d9f.mp3"},{"t":"Ich bin müde, aber glücklich.","en":"I'm tired but happy.","a":"n_8130d7889816.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab Hunger, ich muss essen.","en":"I'm hungry, I need to eat.","a":"n_b090180b25dd.mp3"},{"t":"Ich steh auf und esse.","en":"I get up and eat.","a":"n_27e8a61995a5.mp3"},{"t":"Ich würd gern bestellen, bitte.","en":"I'd like to order, please.","a":"n_78d777c044ce.mp3"},{"t":"Ich weiß, dass du recht hast.","en":"I know you're right.","a":"n_58b8df6d046b.mp3"},{"t":"Ich glaub, du hast recht.","en":"I think you're right.","a":"n_b846d147e722.mp3"},{"t":"Schau, das ist Carlos.","en":"Look, this is Carlos.","a":"n_defcce91bd31.mp3"},{"t":"Ich muss heute lernen.","en":"I have to study today.","a":"n_86d67832c22e.mp3"},{"t":"Nein, das passt.","en":"No, that's fine.","a":"n_0229b58aa08d.mp3"},{"t":"Ich brauch nichts, danke.","en":"I don't need anything, thanks.","a":"n_d861befb539a.mp3"},{"t":"Danke, ist es weit?","en":"Thanks, is it very far?","a":"n_4b0e0723d3f6.mp3"},{"t":"Ich weiß, dass ich's kann.","en":"I know I can do it.","a":"n_7fe45ad44293.mp3"},{"t":"Du schaffst das, ich weiß es.","en":"You can do it, I know it.","a":"n_967c576bed21.mp3"},{"t":"Ich mach's lieber allein, danke.","en":"I'd rather do it alone, thanks.","a":"n_8410f8995d63.mp3"},{"t":"Ich arbeite und esse dann.","en":"I work and then eat.","a":"n_a49a99529960.mp3"},{"t":"Ja, sie heißt Ana.","en":"Yes, her name is Ana.","a":"n_acbd7301e1f9.mp3"},{"t":"Wir müssen jetzt los.","en":"We have to leave now.","a":"n_e5f84a8119bd.mp3"},{"t":"Müssen wir alle gehen?","en":"Do we all have to go?","a":"n_1b33545b8321.mp3"},{"t":"Du hast recht, ich muss mich ausruhen.","en":"You're right, I need to rest.","a":"n_30fc1c1a370d.mp3"},{"t":"Das musst du sehen.","en":"You have to see this.","a":"n_e88d25f724c5.mp3"},{"t":"Die Rechnung, bitte.","en":"The check, please.","a":"n_331a56be943a.mp3"},{"t":"Nein, ich bin aus Mexiko.","en":"No, I'm from Mexico.","a":"n_18a912920716.mp3"},{"t":"Ja, sie ist meine Freundin.","en":"Yes, she's my friend.","a":"n_6452e780a347.mp3"},{"t":"Ja, ich hab echt Hunger.","en":"Yeah, I'm really hungry.","a":"n_dca7e884e46f.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab mehr gegessen als du.","en":"I ate more than you.","a":"n_83773ea3c9be.mp3"},{"t":"Hi, ich heiße Carlos.","en":"Hi, my name is Carlos.","a":"n_6b4abeda687b.mp3"},{"t":"Du musst Geduld haben.","en":"You need to have patience.","a":"n_aa46da98ed25.mp3"},{"t":"Sag ihm, ich bin unterwegs.","en":"Tell him I'm on my way.","a":"n_0f711e3153af.mp3"},{"t":"Sag ihm, es tut mir leid.","en":"Tell him I'm sorry.","a":"n_4f0065c5ec6c.mp3"},{"t":"Freut mich, ich bin Carlos.","en":"Nice to meet you, I'm Carlos.","a":"n_a8d7a6648d8f.mp3"},{"t":"Freut mich, ich heiße Ana.","en":"Nice to meet you, my name is Ana.","a":"n_348aeac67b2a.mp3"},{"t":"Ich muss dir was sagen.","en":"I have to tell you something.","a":"n_2ba769370044.mp3"},{"t":"Schau hierher, nicht dahin.","en":"Look here, not there.","a":"n_acc2c40fb992.mp3"},{"t":"Ich hab zu viel gezahlt, ich weiß.","en":"I paid too much, I know.","a":"n_d710841c1aac.mp3"},{"t":"Ich glaub, ich hab Fieber.","en":"I think I have a fever.","a":"n_dac62c52f323.mp3"}]}